N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 8203.6 - Commitment to confidentiality

State Regulations
(a) Only authorized council personnel shall have direct access to CYIMIS data. All
such personnel shall be informed of, trained in and updated on the
confidentiality laws, policies and practices of CYIMIS. (b) All contractors involved with CYIMIS
shall enter into a written agreement with the council requiring the contractor
to comply with the same confidentiality laws, policies and practices as the
council. (c) Any person willfully
violating or failing to comply with any provisions related to confidentiality
contained in this Part shall be guilty of a misdemeanor. Notes
